ism-and-the-misuse-of-mlk-by-tim-wise/\">\"Fraud fit for a King: Israel, Zionism, and the misuse of MLK\"</a>. <i><a href=\"/wiki/Z_Communications\" title=\"Z Communications\">Z Magazine</a></i><span class=\"reference-accessdate\">. Retrieved <span class=\"nowrap\">December 22,</span> 2017</span>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=Z+Magazine&amp;rft.atitle=Fraud+fit+for+a+King%3A+Israel%2C+Zionism%2C+and+the+misuse+of+MLK&amp;rft.date=2003-01-21&amp;rft.aulast=Wise&amp;rft.aufirst=Tim&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fzcomm.org%2Fzcommentary%2Ffraud-fit-for-a-king-israel-zionism-and-the-misuse-of-mlk-by-tim-wise%2F&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ALetter+to+an+Anti-Zionist+Friend\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-camera-5\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">^ <a href=\"#cite_ref-camera_5-0\"><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href=\"#cite_ref-camera_5-1\"><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a> <a href=\"#cite_ref-camera_5-2\"><sup><i><b>c</b></i></sup></a> <a href=\"#cite_ref-camera_5-3\"><sup><i><b>d</b></i></sup></a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation web\">Green, Lee (January 22, 2002). <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.camera.org/index.asp?x_print=1&amp;x_context=8&amp;x_article=369\">\"CAMERA ALERT: Letter by Martin Luther King a Hoax\"</a>. <i><a href=\"/wiki/Committee_for_Accuracy_in_Middle_East_Reporting_in_America\" title=\"Committee for Accuracy in Middle East Reporting in America\">Committee for Accuracy in Middle East Reporting in America</a></i><span class=\"reference-accessdate\">. Retrieved <span class=\"nowrap\">August 26,</span> 2009</span>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft.jtitle=Committee+for+Accuracy+in+Middle+East+Reporting+in+America&amp;rft.atitle=CAMERA+ALERT%3A+Letter+by+Martin+Luther+King+a+Hoax&amp;rft.date=2002-01-22&amp;rft.aulast=Green&amp;rft.aufirst=Lee&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.camera.org%2Findex.asp%3Fx_print%3D1%26x_context%3D8%26x_article%3D369&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ALetter+to+an+Anti-Zionist+Friend\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-6\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-6\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation news\">Burchill, Julie (December 27, 2003). <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.theguardian.com/world/2003/dec/06/race.uk\">\"Corrections and Clarifications\"</a>. <i><a href=\"/wiki/The_Guardian\" title=\"The Guardian\">The Guardian</a></i>. London<span class=\"reference-accessdate\">. Retrieved <span class=\"nowrap\">September 10,</span> 2009</span>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=The+Guardian&amp;rft.atitle=Corrections+and+Clarifications&amp;rft.date=2003-12-27&amp;rft.aulast=Burchill&amp;rft.aufirst=Julie&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Fworld%2F2003%2Fdec%2F06%2Frace.uk&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ALetter+to+an+Anti-Zionist+Friend\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-kiblawi-youmans-7\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">^ <a href=\"#cite_ref-kiblawi-youmans_7-0\"><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href=\"#cite_ref-kiblawi-youmans_7-1\"><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a> <a href=\"#cite_ref-kiblawi-youmans_7-2\"><sup><i><b>c</b></i></sup></a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation journal\">Kiblawi, Fadi; Youmans, Will (January 17, 2004). <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.counterpunch.org/2004/01/17/the-use-and-abuse-of-martin-luther-king-jr-by-israel-s-apologists/\">\"The Use 